Frequent flyer

26
00:01:24,224 --> 00:01:26,272
Fly often cheap and comfortable

27
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:30,624
In that statement you recognize Key properties of a vision

28
00:01:31,136 --> 00:01:32,160
It should be short

29
00:01:32,672 --> 00:01:34,976
That enables you to focus your development

30
